Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.74,0:00:05.91,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,We were standing outside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:10.24,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Don't go too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.46,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Or else we won't be able to get back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:18.58,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,This is a world that had ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:21.46,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,There is no one here other than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:26.68,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,We were looking for junk that could be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:32.35,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,We have to find our own tools for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.19,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:38.31,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Let's take this back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.50,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Were you scared of being alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.63,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:51.30,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:01.52,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.07,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,They had a gentle smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.87,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are you eating at the cafeteria for lunch again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You just got here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:51.25,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Start right. Otherwise, you'll mess up my rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.68,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Fine. Then I'll start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hello, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.14,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are you eating at the cafeteria for lunch again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You sound so refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:10.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's too refreshing coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You weirded me out with your change in character.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then what am I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:20.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,At the end of the sentence, always add the phrase, "and a toilet seat cover".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That will counter the freshness and make you sound more like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:31.66,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:31.66,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}In Search of a Fake Love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.37,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'll do it one of these days when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:37.17,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What? Mei's staying over at Nagisa-chan's again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're perfectly happy having her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:42.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Since we all love Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:47.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She called ahead and let her parents and school know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Apparently she's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:55.77,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan's a senior, and it's the second semester, yet he still doesn't know what he'll be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:59.07,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm so worried I can't go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:03.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She said she wants to have a good talk with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:08.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san. Do you have a goal or something you want to do? {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I've never thought about it. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:16.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I can't go to college, so I'll find a job and work. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:25.34,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Well, if I had a level-headed girlfriend, too,\NI bet my sister would rest easier. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:26.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's it! {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:34.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Basically, we'll show her that you have\Na girlfriend who you've sworn your life to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mei-chan will stop worrying that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't think you should tell her a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:41.15,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Would something like that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:45.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you know, you're actually not that ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've got a baby face, so you're the type that tickles the maternal instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This school's number one baby face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Baby Sunohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:06:00.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You might end up dating the fake girlfriend for real with this as a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki magic, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.92,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:10.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun. Aren't you just having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:16.69,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are there any obedient girls who'll probably listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're really underhanded, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.56,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I found a perfect candidate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:22.98,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're going to ask her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You don't have to be that surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.79,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Pretend. It's just pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:39.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you can't, you can say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:43.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Since you know well what kind of a guy he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.55,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I can't. It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.43,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.72,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it is so embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.85,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I can't possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please don't cry, Ryou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:02.73,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,When you see something like this,\Ndoesn't it make you want to keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey. If you say something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.41,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Ryou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:18.37,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Was he picking on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.29,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.00,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It wasn't anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:25.63,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You two. What did you do to my cute sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You misunderstand, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.64,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're actually looking for\Na fake girlfriend for Sunohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.72,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,How about we try asking Kyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I doubt she'd say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.39,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yeah, given her character...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:45.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Vicious and hot-headed, says\Nunreasonable things and uses me like a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.78,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I can hear everything you're saying, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.70,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You care to repeat those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:56.08,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll stick my hand down your throat and rip out your vocal cords as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.41,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I apologized, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:04.13,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Your apologizing face pissed me off for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.17,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.09,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Their idiocy will infect us if we stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.22,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.64,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why do guys lack delicacy so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.18,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:24.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Are you really all right, Sunohara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:30.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't worry. He shines brightest when he's being picked on by girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.11,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't say things that'll cause misunderstandings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:38.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But with both Fujibayashi and Kyou down, who else might say yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.21,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,How about asking Tomoyo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.38,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:49.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She's beautiful and takes good care of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think she's a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:53.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'd better not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He's wimping out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't be an idiot! Who's w-wimping out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You had an extra "w" there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Take a deep breath and calm down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.94,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm ready to give birth to a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san, you're panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If you think about it, she and I are fated rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.83,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We would fight every time we bumped into each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.79,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You seem troubled; that's unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:27.42,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.09,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.42,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:38.89,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't want to see you lose to anyone other then me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:48.86,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Deep down, there's mutual respect between those who recognize each other's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:50.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's so touching!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.65,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Therefore I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:58.70,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Tea stains are actually tannin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.99,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Baking soda is often used to wash them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:02.91,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,If you don't have any-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:08.67,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,If you don't have any, vinegar should be fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't ignore me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.34,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Sakagami-san, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.26,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Stay away. It's dangerous to make eye contact with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.01,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't talk of me like I'm an animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:22.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoyo-san. Please listen to what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.14,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Oh, Furukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:26.31,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Yesterday's baseball game was fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:27.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You looked really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.57,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,It's actually my first time calling you Furukawa-san, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.28,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Was that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.66,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Could you two not carry on a conversation without me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.08,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What, you were still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:47.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He has a favor to ask. Could you hear him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:54.17,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You guys come asking for favors a lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:58.30,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm really troubled right now, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.30,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You look carefree to me, as you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:03.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.60,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Exactly. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:10.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,No! You're supposed to say, "I don't want to see you lose to anyone other then me."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.98,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I've never considered saying that in my life, not even the slightest bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.32,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Just say it! Or else we can't advance the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:21.95,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't want to see you lose to anyone other than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,"Lose"? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.74,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,How about we-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.96,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,If he wanted to fight, he should have said so immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.29,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,See you, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:33.79,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.92,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,That was so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.63,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,As expected of Sakagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.76,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.76,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're so kind, Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:50.06,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I want to be of help to my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.65,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tell me what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:58.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If you're dating, I think you would hang out and do all sorts of fun things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.82,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:00.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.16,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Look at what you made her do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:11.29,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Didn't the violin get fixed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.42,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yes. It makes better sound than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's actually gotten worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:20.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Was it really all right, Sunohara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She agreed to act for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:27.64,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I don't have the willpower to make it through that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We still have one hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Miyazawa, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.78,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, Furukawa-san, Sunohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:38.94,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, it has been a while, Miyazawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yukine-chan, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:47.58,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yeah, you look like you'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.29,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.29,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,To act as a girlfriend, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.38,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It sounds difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.30,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:00.84,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'll lead you along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So please. Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.89,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I've been listening for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:12.02,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are to ask such a thing of our Yuki-nee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"Our Yuki-nee?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Miyazawa-san, who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.07,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,He's my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:22.53,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,There is a small issue, so he is hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.11,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Let me tell you clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:28.03,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,If you cause any trouble for Yuki-nee, we won't let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.99,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Do you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:36.25,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Crap, I wasn't supposed to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.09,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yuki-nee, if anything happens, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:42.76,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I'll dash over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.63,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.93,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,You need to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.10,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I need to excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:55.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:58.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looks like she has some things to deal with, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm going to leave you two here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I have to help make dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:11.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good luck, Sunohara-san. {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:17.58,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,"Good luck" she says, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:21.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It wasn't right to ask for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's put out a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:25.88,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:30.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter, since you're going to charm her, anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.10,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,First, you have to flatter the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:40.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And, girls these days like to keep secrets,\Nso let her know that secrets are safe with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:45.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Lastly, using group psychology to your advantage, appeal saying that everyone does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.78,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.37,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey there cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.12,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:53.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Do you have some time right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:56.41,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It'd be great if you would even just listen to what I need to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.75,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I actually have a good part-time job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.09,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I won't say your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:07.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And I'll keep it a secret to your parents, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:11.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Everyone's doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.10,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That makes me sound like I'm scouting her for something sketchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.64,San,San,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.77,San,San,0,0,0,,Are you having some trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.03,San,San,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:28.90,San,San,0,0,0,,If that's the case, would you allow me to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Sanae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:36.37,San,San,0,0,0,,It's for none other than Mei-chan's brother's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.91,San,San,0,0,0,,If I can be of help, then I'll gladly do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:41.46,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki. She's Nagisa-chan's older sister, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah, right. I said something like that yesterday, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:53.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Crap! As expected from Nagisa-chan's sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:56.14,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She's so freaking hot when I see her up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is interesting, so I'll let him keep thinking wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.98,San,San,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.23,San,San,0,0,0,,Would I not be suitable?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.69,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:09.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But wouldn't it be too obvious that you're a fake girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.36,San,San,0,0,0,,It'll be all right. I'll go in a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then you're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:18.04,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes. I look forward to acting with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.45,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:23.04,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yahoo! Yahoo! Yahoo! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.29,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You have a girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:28.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Someone I've sworn my future to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.76,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She's really beautiful and level-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:36.56,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm not living aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:40.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm walking up the stairs to adulthood one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.73,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Let me see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.19,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Introduce me to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:49.48,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,As your younger sister, I want to know what kind of person you're going to marry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:53.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okay. Then I'll ask her what her schedule's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.79,San,San,0,0,0,,The Theater Club has many costumes, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:06.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'll meet Mei-chan the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So tomorrow will be a practice run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.76,San,San,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It feels complicated to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:18.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,My mom is my classmate's girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara's really hyped over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:27.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He thinks of you as Nagisa's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.73,San,San,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.82,San,San,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to flatter you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:39.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you reconsider this, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:46.42,San,San,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san has been on\Nmy mind since the baseball game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:52.42,San,San,0,0,0,,He looks clumsy and makes many mistakes, but I think he's actually a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:57.93,San,San,0,0,0,,With a push, I think he can start walking a better path.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:02.68,San,San,0,0,0,,I want to help him get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:08.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okay. If you think so, then I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.82,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let me say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:15.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We need to keep this a secret from the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:16.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:22.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san might be doing it for the sake of helping others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:27.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,but knowing him, he might fly into\Na jealous rage and turn Sunohara into mincemeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:33.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,For Sunohara's safety, we need to keep this a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san's really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Watching him is pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:52.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're in love with Mom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You idiot! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:57.74,San,San,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.16,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:05.33,San,San,0,0,0,,It would be strange to call you "Sunohara-kun" when we're dating, so I'll call you "Youhei-kun".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Y-Y-Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.08,San,San,0,0,0,,Youhei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.88,San,San,0,0,0,,I look forward to spending time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.38,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Crap! She called me "Youhei-kun"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.76,San,San,0,0,0,,Shall we begin with walking next to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:23.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Y-Y-Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:32.15,San,San,0,0,0,,You can come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.36,San,San,0,0,0,,Since we're dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Crap! I smelled something sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.41,San,San,0,0,0,,How about we hold hands, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Crap! They're so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't come reporting to me each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:57.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is that really making him go down the right path?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It feels complicated to me, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And so the day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san's here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, call out to him from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet he'll think it's his girl and be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:21.40,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Then I'll give it a little try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.20,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:30.00,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,No, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:30.46,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,MEI?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san, what are all of these cans?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This is part of my strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She'll see this when she gets here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.59,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.63,San,San,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:46.60,San,San,0,0,0,,You waited for me this long?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.98,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You see how it goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're really underhanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:56.94,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This is the game in the name of love guys play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:01.03,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a boy love game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you know, that implies something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.03,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Crap. I drank too much and nature calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.79,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,If it's this messy, it'll be a bother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's clean it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.21,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.51,San,San,0,0,0,,Let me help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:27.22,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:27.76,San,San,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.48,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, are you blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:47.66,San,San,0,0,0,,Youhei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:52.62,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Did I make you wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:55.92,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.92,San,San,0,0,0,,Not at all. I just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.13,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,This person is my brother's girlfriend?
